Place super-resolution TFLite models here:
- sr_model_2x.tflite  (2x upscaling model)
- sr_model_3x.tflite  (3x upscaling model)
- sr_model_4x.tflite  (4x upscaling model)

Model input format: float32[1, height, width, 3] (RGB, range 0-1)
Model output format: float32[1, height*scale, width*scale, 3]

If no model is found, the app uses a high-quality
classical upscaling pipeline (Lanczos + AI sharpening).
